{"tid":1577652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推爆新屋嶺] 新屋嶺嘅義士唔係condom!!","createTime":"2019-09-17T20:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T10:36:03.000Z","uid":104507,"like":78,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"d5ce50942885c47035ea1d2600772b801dc9e00d","tid":1577652,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T20:51:36.000Z","msg":"佢地係入面所受嘅苦 黑警一定要10倍奉還<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[手動轉]<br />\n<br />\n點解我一直強調新屋嶺應被優先處理？<br />\n因為好不容易爭取到國際關注香港情況之後，發生響太子嘅事件係佢哋眼中，充其量都係「警察執法時不幸有市民死亡」，但新屋嶺則明顯係「殺人輪姦集中營」！<br />\n唔好忘記：太子站死者數目有限而新屋嶺死亡數目係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>與日俱增</strong></span>！而且太子站事件國際社會冇咁好理由干預，但新屋嶺可以係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>反人類罪行</strong></span></span>，<strong>國際社會比較大機會介入</strong>！！<br />\n所有人嘅公道都需要爭取，但明唔明白先後輕重之別？？<br />\n#生人要去救#救人<br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺唔比人入都夠恐怖<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">到底咩原因先唔比啲太平紳士入</span></span><br />\n大家認為唔洗推爆嗎？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n建議應舉行與新屋嶺有關嘅集會或遊行<br />\n全部人推爆新屋嶺<br />\n一定要迫黑警對外公開新屋嶺<br />\n同831太子CCTV同理</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為新屋嶺嘅野係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">切切實實</span></span></strong>發生咗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">加上新屋嶺post經常性推唔郁</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外附上一張圖<br />\n大家加以反思<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/agWtJoz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FagWtJoz.jpg&h=0626c037&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3a14ff83297444eac96a0ec887fd9023fc83b5b","tid":1577652,"uid":104507,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:09:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新屋嶺 係鬼屋<br />\n<br />\n義士唔係condom</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個大家都認同 唔可以齋係<span style=\"color: red;\">口號</span><br />\n不過 我地真係對新屋嶺係無辦法<br />\n佢地留得係新屋嶺一日就真係辛苦一日<br />\n強姦 虐打 酷刑<br />\n我地都幾肯定日日都發生緊<br />\n<br />\n先唔講要釋放義士<br />\n呢個係五大訴求之一<br />\n肯定要嘅<br />\n但大家都知短期內 真係無機會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可唔可以集齊人馬 要求<span style=\"color: red;\">轉倉</span>？</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">示威又好 簽名又好 集會又好</span></span></strong> <del>衝去新屋嶺又好啦</del><br />\n可以點做？唔可以畀佢地繼續受不人道對待<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以搞次 係針對新屋嶺？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573912</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好得個講字 嗌口號就算<br />\n我地真係要做出嚟<br />\n要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救人</span></span>呀<br />\n救手足呀 佢地等緊我地救㗎！<br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺申請禁制令搞成點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573440</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b989233e45f884f22d72adbc55ef3f28942fdb4","tid":1577652,"uid":104507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:10:15.000Z","msg":"瞓醒再推"},{"pid":"35f806947dcef319f7de8340bd38d1cdb4e1d940","tid":1577652,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:11:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6aebc29205a14b52495f5626154ff1cac27c0c28","tid":1577652,"uid":18739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:11:53.000Z","msg":"要集中打依條線"},{"pid":"614dd482ac2e0e9d1e89921500bb116381abbf3d","tid":1577652,"uid":245250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:12:33.000Z","msg":"推 除左再傳新屋嶺發生咩事 救人出黎最緊要"},{"pid":"cd92c43dfa6a53f4ce45988ffdb3d4fd648ba3f0","tid":1577652,"uid":104507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:15:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要針對已證實發生咗嘅新屋嶺事件<br />\n<br />\n【不見天日　不時傳出慘叫】<br />\n<br />\n【嚴重骨折　警方全沒紀錄】<br />\n<br />\n要求服哮喘藥遭拒<br />\n<br />\n粗言穢語不斷喝罵<br />\n<br />\n壹週刊：女被捕者目睹血人一字排開　<br />\n新屋嶺私刑場　黑太陽811</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190916/20768982\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F20768982&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5CcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=f47500f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190916%2F20768982&h=b2b1f454\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190916/20768982</a>"},{"pid":"86166b613170fa7c2830e1686e79fe09291f2758","tid":1577652,"uid":14459,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:15:06.000Z","msg":"每日諗起新屋嶺真係做乜都冇心機<br />\n希望快啲救得翻佢地出嚟"},{"pid":"18eda6d73336242ed85b94d8046f1e47c481a71b","tid":1577652,"uid":224253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:17:26.000Z","msg":"推 我覺得搵次搞果到 越早越好 你試諗下依加每一日都有手足係入面比人打比人輪 好想有次夢見自己去拆場救人"},{"pid":"6bdd6f6e4d3d5b86348b646ce047fa01c63777b7","tid":1577652,"uid":104507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:18:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新屋嶺拘留所多名被捕者受傷　北區醫院護士透露部分人有不尋常瘀傷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/284560/【移交逃犯修例】新屋嶺拘留所多名被捕者受傷%E3%80%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F284560%2F%E3%80%90%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%8B%E5%B6%BA%E6%8B%98%E7%95%99%E6%89%80%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%80%85%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%25E3%2580%2580%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5CcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=b4302f5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/284560/【移交逃犯修例】新屋嶺拘留所多名被捕者受傷%E3%80%80/</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"b56285386b67c7f834e65f5b69c22c11b2d559db","tid":1577652,"uid":224253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:20:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a8a1185d544f0b43cb31f15a439ab073cf99a2a","tid":1577652,"uid":104507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:21:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有北區醫院護士透露，部分被捕人骨折情況嚴重。新屋嶺16歲抗爭者 成隻手只剩一層皮連住<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EH8G3Bo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEH8G3Bo.jpg&h=e01783b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lam777.com/view2/6043/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flam777.com%2Fview2%2F6043%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5CcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=6b670884\" target=\"_blank\">http://lam777.com/view2/6043/</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"640d3053aa7ddee5ed65aa406fdc465dfe1022cc","tid":1577652,"uid":224253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:21:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c869278873c20be6f3d63fc34a8f781209f49fa","tid":1577652,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:22:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>義士唔係condom!<br />\n香港人唔可以習慣<br />\n唔可以善忘</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"53d22e08ecb59c1a0ca677d10eb6e1d19fc22aff","tid":1577652,"uid":224253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T21:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0763b8adc522f2307831d748b1263da2edb79d5","tid":1577652,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20