br />\n因為好不容易爭取到國際關注香港情況之後，發生響太子嘅事件係佢哋眼中，充其量都係「警察執法時不幸有市民死亡」，但新屋嶺則明顯係「殺人輪姦集中營」！<br />\n唔好忘記：太子站死者數目有限而新屋嶺死亡數目係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>與日俱增</strong></span>！而且太子站事件國際社會冇咁好理由干預，但新屋嶺可以係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>反人類罪行</strong></span></span>，<strong>國際社會比較大機會介入</strong>！！<br />\n所有人嘅公道都需要爭取，但明唔明白先後輕重之別？？<br />\n#生人要去救#救人<br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺唔比人入都夠恐怖<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">到底咩原因先唔比啲太平紳士入</span></span><br />\n大家認為唔洗推爆嗎？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n建議應舉行與新屋嶺有關嘅集會或遊行<br />\n全部人推爆新屋嶺<br />\n一定要迫黑警對外公開新屋嶺<br />\n同831太子CCTV同理</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為新屋嶺嘅野係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">切切實實</span></span></strong>發生咗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">加上新屋嶺post經常性推唔郁</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外附上一張圖<br />\n大家加以反思<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/agWtJoz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FagWtJoz.jpg&h=0626c037&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:32:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"beb9a4e0bd15e6f198416115b1a3e7079110f505","tid":1577652,"uid":35632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b97144137ae45e7afd1c8a1ff91fe0917a0dbcd","tid":1577652,"uid":210587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5ce50942885c47035ea1d2600772b801dc9e00d","tid":1577652,"uid":104507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T20:51:36.000Z","msg":"佢地係入面所受嘅苦 黑警一定要10倍奉還<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" cla