5,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:59:43.000Z","msg":"借貴寶地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1）警察<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">衰野太多，好難一張文宣講晒</span></span></strong><br />\n2）我地前線手足都開始<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反擊得勁D，反擊畫面</span></span></strong>又會被現在好落力打國際戰的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府拎黎大造文章，條片正好俾外國能更好地體諒我地</span></span></strong><br />\n3）更好利用一些<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心</span></strong></span><br />\n4）微電影，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"e533c82843d787654afb3a9f1e889939ad9ad4b7","tid":1577652,"uid":137833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:00:40.000Z","msg":"推 唔好再送手足入去啦"},{"pid":"78e39f68917fe9594c1153832bb645ab5137b892","tid":1577652,"uid":218081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:01:48.000Z","msg":"on9黑警<br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺手足，大家記得你地，大家幫手推一推新屋嶺post,多d人討論先係做實事第一步，要多多多人關注注注注，推到泛民做嘢，太平紳士做嘢"},{"pid":"951feccdab794d0240aeaf76293fa66cb3313eb6","tid":1577652,"uid":171385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"164eb28f8b01e50c220cb4238d476c3297a791ec","tid":1577652,"uid":4448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T07:3